summary: QUESTION: IS THERE ANY ACTIONS OR EVALUATIONS TAKING PLACE ON AUTO HEADLIGHTS?  I FIND THE NEW HEADLIGHTS TO BE OVERLY BRIGHT, DISTRACTING AND AT TIMES BLINDING.  SOME OF THEM ARE EQUIVALENT TO SOMEBODY DRIVING WITH THEIR HIGH-BEAMS ON.  I HAVE HEARD NUMEROUS OTHER PEOPLE COMPLAIN - FOR THE PERSON BEHIND THE WHEEL THEY ARE GREAT.  FOR THE PERSON SEEING THEM HEAD-ON THEY POSE A SERIOUS SAFETY RISK.   *NLM
